DDEESSCCRRIIPPTTIIOONN
       ppeerrff is an XView program that  reports  kernel  statistics
       for a given hhoosstt (or for the localhost if no host is spec-
       ified). The program is a frontend to the rstatd(8) daemon.

       The  displayed window consists of one or more fields, each
       showing a specified parameter. The name of  the  parameter
       and  of  its components are shown in the lower left corner
       of the field, the maximum value of the visible data in the
       lower right corner.


